refsect2.para:
An example test case for a test core and its expected output:

  [Retro Reftest]
  Path=/test
  Core=/app/lib/libretro/test_libretro.so

  [Options]
  test_aspect=4:3;16:9;
  test_samplerate=30000;20000;
  test_opt0=false;true;
  test_opt1=0;
  test_opt2=0;1;foo;3;

  [Frame 0]
  State=Refresh
  Video=test.png

An example test case for a Sega Genesis emulator and its expected output:
[Retro Reftest] Path=/blastem/240pSuite Core=/app/lib/libretro/blastem_libretro.so Medias=240pTestSuite-v15.gen;
[Frame 150] Video=blastem.240pSuite.150.png
